data.description: Welcome Home! This beautiful home was professionally remodeled to the last detail. Extreme temperatures won't bother you with the brand new HVAC system. If you are worried about the rain it also has a new roof, and inside you will find fresh paint, new doors, new cabinets in kitchen and bathrooms all toped with elegant quartz countertops. Enjoy a bright and fresh home with new light fixtures and fans. Hurry up so you can be the first one to make use of the brand new flooring and upscale bathrooms.
